[Git] Interactive Rebase

You are tasked with restructuring and managing a Git commit history to ensure a clean and meaningful commit log. The goal is to automate the process of squashing redundant commits, updating commit messages, and reverting unnecessary changes using non-interactive rebase and revert operations.


