Create and switch to a new branch named cleanup-history from the main branch.

Make three commits:


Commit 1: Add the text "Typo fix" to a file named README.md and commit with the message: "Fix typos in README"

Commit 2: Create a file named dependencies.txt with the content "Updated dependencies" and commit with the message: "Update project dependencies"

Commit 3: Add the text "Formatted README" to the existing README.md file and commit with the message: "Improve README formatting"

Squash commits using non-interactive rebase:


Squash the first commit (Fix typos in README) and the third commit (Improve README formatting) into a single commit.


